{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Permissions","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Permissions","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Permissions_API\">Permissions API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Permissions\"><code>Permissions</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Permissions/query\"><code>query()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Permissions/revoke\"><code>revoke()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Permissions API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/permissions\"><code>Navigator.permissions</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/PermissionStatus\"><code>PermissionStatus</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator/permissions\"><code>WorkerNavigator.permissions</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>これは<a href=\"/ja/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\">実験的な機能</a>です。</strong><br>本番で使用する前に<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">ブラウザー互換性一覧表</a>をチェックしてください。</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Permissions_API\">Permissions API</a> の <code>Permissions</code> インターフェイスは、パーミッションの照会および取り消しのためのメソッドなど、コアとなる Permission API 機能を提供します。</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"メソッド","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"permissions.query\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Permissions/query\"><code>Permissions.query()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>特定の API のパーミッションの状態を返します。</dd>\n <dt id=\"permissions.request\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>Permissions.request()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>特定の API を使用するパーミッションを要求します。 これは現在どのブラウザーもサポートしていません。</dd>\n <dt id=\"permissions.revoke\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Permissions/revoke\"><code>Permissions.revoke()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>特定の API に現在設定されているパーミッションを取り消します。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>permissions<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">query</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token literal-property property\">name</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">'geolocation'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">result</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>result<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>state <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">'granted'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">showLocalNewsWithGeolocation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>result<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>state <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">'prompt'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">showButtonToEnableLocalNews</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// パーミッションが拒否された場合は何もしないでください。</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/permissions/#permissions-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Permissions<br><small lang=\"ja\">Permissions の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_support","isH3":false,"query":"api.Permissions","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Permissions/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"メソッド","id":"methods"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specification"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_support"}],"summary":"Permissions API の Permissions インターフェイスは、パーミッションの照会および取り消しのためのメソッドなど、コアとなる Permission API 機能を提供します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Permissions","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Permissions","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/permissions","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/permissions/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Permissions","title":"Permissions"}],"pageTitle":"Permissions - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}